{"tid":437994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰未澄清是否獨立  中央政府即將接管統治","createTime":"2017-10-16T13:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T07:15:56.000Z","uid":62257,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9d5194b4ead61d96e28be95d4bad8292e246af","tid":437994,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201710160177-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201710160177-1.aspx&d=iHe0AXGv8ycdxYU%2FahLYx8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f4ade00c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201710160177-1.aspx</a><br />\n（中央社馬德里16日綜合外電報導）加泰隆尼亞自治區主席普伊格蒙特（Carles Puigdemont）今天沒有澄清他上週是否宣布加泰隆尼亞獨立，這為中央政府接管和直接統治加泰隆尼亞鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，西班牙總理拉荷義（Mariano Rajoy）要求普伊格蒙特在今天當地時間早上10時之前澄清意向，如果他堅持要脫離西班牙，19日之前還可以改變心意。倘若他選擇獨立，馬德里將停止加泰隆尼亞自治權。<br />\n<br />\n加泰隆尼亞媒體已公開普伊格蒙特寫給拉荷義的信，普伊格蒙特在信中並沒有直接回答是否要獨立的問題，反而要求兩人應該儘快會面，在未來兩個月展開對話。<br />\n<br />\n普伊格蒙特在信中表示：「儘管發生了這一切，我們仍誠摯地提出對話要求。」（譯者：中央社陳昱婷）1061016"},{"pid":"81dcf4d2f8d2f241711ab512e7e7fcd2d66eed5c","tid":437994,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:18:01.000Z","msg":"左膠..."},{"pid":"5ad4edab90bebad3e3f17ab1475fcd73f3f6b934","tid":437994,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=239627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D239627&d=iHe0AXGv8ycdxYU%2FahLYx8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0d2fc84c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D239627&h=0a80b28b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=239627</a><br />\n2小時前<br />\n【Now新聞台】西班牙中央政府要求加泰羅尼亞自治區政府澄清是否已宣布獨立的限期屆滿，自治區主席普伊格蒙特並未給予明確答案，中央政府要求對方必須在周四前確認並無宣布獨立。<br />\n<br />\n普伊格蒙特在回覆首相拉霍伊的信件中，並無明確回覆是否已經宣布自治區獨立，只是提出兩人應該在未來兩個月展開對話，討論加泰羅尼亞局勢，尋求雙方均同意的解決方法。<br />\n<br />\n副首相薩恩斯德聖瑪麗亞在限期後見傳媒，對普伊格蒙特並無回覆中央政府的問題感到遺憾，要求對方在周四早上確認並無宣布加泰羅尼亞獨立，否則中央政府或會引用憲法第155條收回加泰羅尼亞自治權，最終是否要走到這一步，決定權在普伊格蒙特手上。<br />\n<br />\n她同時強調中央政府並無拒絕對話，但任何對話都必須在法律框架內進行。"},{"pid":"a0372b060b5a65bdf1c7fe0d2a7d6e8dbf38fea3","tid":437994,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024606dc93a78bfcdc50fb6795ea59709d90e078","tid":437994,"uid":33770,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"收回自冶權一定重挫加泰經濟<br />\n兩邊都冇好處"},{"pid":"87ea495d30d397de18bccad0ffd6a31606ce5a9d","tid":437994,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"687c7544f9e29670ffd42d32019f0107d3a218be","tid":437994,"uid":35815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:06:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1b327794ed1b778bbcc16320a85d9c6e8944727","tid":437994,"uid":46644,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c4f682d15e637bda2bbe101817fd7a725590612","tid":437994,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f361cb19da0f70cac66ceacaf120f9c212cf9534","tid":437994,"uid":16970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:32:11.000Z","msg":"一場遊戲一場夢."},{"pid":"4546f847b875028e855a98eca17e595d1dc5dd36","tid":437994,"uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你估鳩叫獨立，唔洗付出代價呀</blockquote><br />\n借個位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">站務台投訴三色貓</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/430728/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nOct 15近期活躍五毛<br />\n1三色貓<br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n3法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國<br />\n4十卜ching<br />\n5newlife<br />\n6侵B<br />\n7返六日唔撚易<br />\n8dewi<br />\n9bb chu<br />\n10優美開始"},{"pid":"102829c8cbbd10589ea80c05253714853db5df7c","tid":437994,"uid":61105,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"其實你搞得獨立就預左會被人打壓，個日應該食住個勢宣佈獨立，而家勢又無左，揀邊樣都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0b7be18907d77cbe253b5c9bd50b3aa6b763a4","tid":437994,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e683939dd2b9c07cf64990fe44dfe0e7fb062dd9","tid":437994,"uid":4258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你搞得獨立就預左會被人打壓，個日應該食住個勢宣佈獨立，而家勢又無左，揀邊樣都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實無分別, 無大國承認又無軍隊, 結局一早預定"},{"pid":"88c8b5caf23cfdd6a8134e87b5340af1d68348f3","tid":437994,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你搞得獨立就預左會被人打壓，個日應該食住個勢宣佈獨立，而家勢又無左，揀邊樣都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實無分別, 無大國承認又無軍隊, 結局一早預定</blockquote><br />\n垃圾歐盟，成班偽善左膠應該仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068a86c1935a29f541d03097d408868fc011a5bf","tid":437994,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你搞得獨立就預左會被人打壓，個日應該食住個勢宣佈獨立，而家勢又無左，揀邊樣都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實無分別, 無大國承認又無軍隊, 結局一早預定</blockquote><br />\n就算係都寧願宣佈獨立左先，輸都輸得有骨氣，最多咪比西班牙拉晒坐監，好過而家畏首畏尾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5677fb9254ed87f6df1589ed340abcb680